content: Is this an unpopular opinion? I only want to support, work with and be influenced by fully doxxed influencers. Trust and Capability is a standard I want to push for in this space. #NFT #Leadership #Accountability

What I'm looking for in an NFT project:

TRANSPARENCY: Who are you and what is your exp? Why X price and Y supply? Budget/expense report?

ACCOUNTABILITY: What are you going to do if things go wrong? If FUD? FP < MP? If no sellout?

VALUE: Can you provide this before your launch?
And I call upon all the investors and consumers out there in the Elrond NFT space to ask this level of accountability from any project that promises utilities.

I have multiple projects I want to work on, but I need to finish my first before doing anything new!

I mainly posted this for my own accountability, but I wanted to keep you all updated as well :)
